    <title>用 Karabiner Elements 自定义你的键盘</title>
    <link href="https://www.aranne.me/posts/vermilo-keyboard-with-karabiner-elements/"/>
    <id>https://www.aranne.me/posts/vermilo-keyboard-with-karabiner-elements/</id>
